    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wagons, originally horse- or mule-drawn and later motorized, usually square-box in shape with a detachable top or trap-door at the rear which may be used as a luggage rack. Used for passengers or cargo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
